data.text:
Becoming a swimwear model needs a lot of hard work and talent. These models have managed to reach the position of top 10 swimwear models. Irina Shayk tops them all taking the place of number one.

Top 10 Swimwear Models

Irina Shayk

Alessandra Ambrosio

Emily Ratajkowski

Ashley Graham

Candice Swanepoel

Rosie Huntington-Whiteley

Jasmine Tookes

Lais Ribeiro

Nina Agdal

Lupe Fuentes

Swimwear Models

1. Irina Shayk

RAED MORE: Miss World 2019 Is Coming To London: Date and Venue revealed

Irina Valeryevna Shaykhlislamova known as Irina Shayk is thirty-three-year-old Russian model. She received international recognition in 2007. She has just been named the world’s top swimwear model. She was ranked highest paid model in 2012 in Forbes List.

Born: January 6, 1986 (age 33 years), Yemanzhelinsk, Russia

Height: 1.78 m

Nationality: Russian

Hair color: Dark brown

Children: Lea De Seine Shayk Cooper

Instagram

2. Alessandra Ambrosio

Alessandra Ambrosio the 38-year-old model is best known for her work with Victoria’s Secret. The Brazilian model and actress and also one of the top 10 swimwear models, she was a runner up. She has her own swimwear brand called GAL Floripa

Born: April 11, 1981 (age 38 years), Erechim, State of Rio Grande do Sul, Brazil

Height: 1.76 m

Full name: Alessandra Corine Ambrósio

Partner(s): Jamie Mazur (2005–2018); Nicolo Oddi (2018–present)

Children: Noah Phoenix Ambrosio Mazur, Anja Louise Ambrosio Mazur

Instagram

3. Emily Ratajkowski

Twenty-eight-year-old Emily Ratajkowski won the third place. Emily Ratajkowski is an American actress and model.

Born: June 7, 1991 (age 28 years), Westminster, London, United Kingdom

Height: 1.7 m

Spouse: Sebastian Bear-McClard (m. 2018)

Nationality: American, British

Parents: Kathleen Balgley, John David Ratajkowski

Instagram

4. Ashley Graham

Plus size model Ashley Graham took the fourth position. The thirty-one-year-old American model has appeared in fashion magazines covers such as Vogue, Harper’s Bazaar, Glamour, and Elle

Born: October 30, 1987 (age 31 years), Lincoln, Nebraska, United States

Height: 1.75 m

Nationality: American

Spouse: Justin Ervin (m. 2010)

Parents: Linda Graham

Instagram

5. Candice Swanepoel

Thirty-year-old Candice Swanepoel is at fifth place. She is a South African supermodel and philanthropist who is known for her work with Victoria’s Secret.

Born: October 20, 1988 (age 30 years), Mooi River, South Africa

Height: 1.77 m

Partner(s): Hermann Nicoli (2005–present)

Hair color: Blonde

Children: Ariel Swanepoel Nicoli, Anaca Nicoli

Parents: Eileen Swanepoel, Willem Swanepoel

Instagram

6. Rosie Huntington-Whiteley

Rosie Huntington-Whiteley the thirty-two-year-old is in the sixth place. The English model, actress, designer, and businesswoman. She is best known for her work for lingerie retailer Victoria’s Secret.

Born: April 18, 1987 (age 32 years), Plymouth, United Kingdom

Height: 1.75 m

Partner: Jason Statham (2010–)

Movies and TV shows: Transformers: Dark of the Moon, Mad Max: Fury Road, The Victoria’s Secret Fashion Show

Children: Jack Oscar Statham

Parents: Charles Andrew Huntington-Whiteley, Fiona Huntington-Whiteley

Instagram

7. Jasmine Tookes

Jasmine Tookes, the twenty-eight-year-old is an American model and Victoria’s Secret Angel. She is in the seventh position.

Born: February 1, 1991 (age 28 years), Huntington Beach, California, United States

Height: 1.75 m

Nationality: American

Hair color: Dark brown

Agency: IMG Models

Parents: Sean Tookes, Cary Robinson

Instagram

8. Lais Ribeiro

This twenty-eight-year-old Brazilian model is at eighth place. She is best known for her work as Victoria’s Secret Angel.

Born: October 5, 1990 (age 28 years), Miguel Alves, State of Piauí, Brazil

Height: 1.84 m

Nationality: Brazilian

Children: Alexandre Ribeiro

Parents: José Ribeiro de Oliveira Filho, Socorro Oliveira

Agencies: Women Management, Next Management, Munich Models

Instagram

9. Nina Agdal

10. Lupe Fuentes

Lupe Fuentes is at tenth position on the list of top 10 swimwear models. She is a Colombian house music producer, DJ, and former pornographic actress. She has been married to singer and actor Evan Seinfeld since 2011

Born: January 27, 1987 (age 32 years), Cali, Colombia

Height: 1.45 m
